column1: Rosary will be said at 5:00 PM Sunday at Rector Funeral Home Osage Chapel with deacon Pablo Morales officiating. Mass of the Christian Burial will be at 2:00 PM Monday at St. Laurence Catholic Church with Father Antonio Galindo
